trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content"></xref> Web server control.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ContentDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> object for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> objeto para este designer.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ContentDesigner> objects add <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem> elements to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content> control.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the control can be resized on the visual designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o controle pode ser redimensionado na superfície de design visual.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time from the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a marcação que é usada para representar o controle em tempo de design especificado <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: The markup generated by GetDesignTimeHtml includes region identifiers.
trans-unit.target: A marcação gerada por GetDesignTimeHtml inclui identificadores de região.

trans-unit.source: GetDesignTimeHtml should add <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion> elements to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> specified by the `regions` parameter.
trans-unit.target: GetDesignTimeHtml deve adicionar <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>elementos para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>especificado pelo `regions` parâmetro.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> associated with the design-time markup generated by GetDesignTimeHtml.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> associado com a marcação de tempo de design gerada pelo GetDesignTimeHtml.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: A marcação que é usada para representar o controle em tempo de design.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o conteúdo do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> elements are defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> and the design-time markup contains region identifiers, the GetEditableDesignerRegionContent method is used to return the content for each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>elementos são definidos na <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>e a marcação de tempo de design contém identificadores de região, o método GetEditableDesignerRegionContent é usado para retornar o conteúdo para cada <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>no <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection></xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> from which to get the content.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> da qual obter o conteúdo.

trans-unit.source: The persistence string for the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A cadeia de caracteres de persistência para o conteúdo do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the inner markup of the control.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a marcação interna do controle.

trans-unit.source: A region is not a property of the control, so for persistent content, this method must return the inner HTML markup of the control.
trans-unit.target: Uma região não é uma propriedade do controle, para que conteúdo persistente, esse método deve retornar a marcação HTML interna do controle.

trans-unit.source: The inner markup of the control.
trans-unit.target: A marcação interna do controle.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, allows a designer to change or remove items from the set of properties that it exposes through a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituído em uma classe derivada, permite que um designer alterar ou remover itens do conjunto de propriedades que expõe por meio de um <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: This method provides a way to change or remove items within the dictionary of properties that are exposed through a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método fornece uma maneira de alterar ou remover itens no dicionário de propriedades que são expostas por meio de <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are the names of the properties.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de propriedades são os nomes das propriedades.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Os objetos são do tipo <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: In this overridden method, the designer clears all properties except <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ID%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Neste método substituído, o designer limpa todas as propriedades, exceto <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ID%2A>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ID%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Content.ContentPlaceHolderID%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"></xref> objects that represent the properties of the class of the component.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"> </xref> objetos que representam as propriedades da classe do componente.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of properties are property names.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de propriedades são nomes de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, allows a designer to add items to the set of events that it exposes through a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituído em uma classe derivada, permite que um designer adicionar itens ao conjunto de eventos que expõe por meio de um <xref href="System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: This method provides a way to add items to the dictionary of events that a designer exposes through a <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método fornece uma maneira de adicionar itens ao dicionário de eventos que expõe um designer por meio de <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of events are the names of the events.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de eventos são os nomes dos eventos.

trans-unit.source: The objects are of type <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Os objetos são do tipo <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: In this overridden method, the designer clears all events for this control.
trans-unit.target: Neste método substituído, o designer limpa todos os eventos para este controle.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor"></xref> objects that represent the events of the class of the component.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor"> </xref> objetos que representam os eventos da classe do componente.

trans-unit.source: The keys in the dictionary of events are event names.
trans-unit.target: As chaves no dicionário de eventos são nomes de evento.

trans-unit.source: Sets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Define o conteúdo do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Developers will typically persist the content to the control or property that represents the region.
trans-unit.target: Os desenvolvedores geralmente serão mantido o conteúdo para o controle ou uma propriedade que representa a região.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> elements are defined in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> and the design-time markup contains region identifiers, the SetEditableDesignerRegionContent method is used to set the content for each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> in the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Se <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>elementos são definidos no <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>e a marcação de tempo de design contém identificadores de região, o método SetEditableDesignerRegionContent é usado para definir o conteúdo para cada <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>em <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> in which to set the content.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> no qual definir o conteúdo.

trans-unit.source: The persistence string for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> content.
trans-unit.target: A cadeia de caracteres de persistência para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> conteúdo.
